  "markup": "\u003Cp style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;\u0022 class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003EOur policy regarding the hiring of relatives and managing personal relationships is to avoid potential conflicts of interest, ensure fairness, and maintain a professional work environment. While we value you, direct reporting relationships between relatives or individuals in close personal relationships are generally avoided to prevent favoritism, perceived conflicts, or supervisory challenges. This policy aims to protect the integrity of our hiring and management processes.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E"
}]]></Value>
